# Pipeline Conventions

## SBOM & Security
- SBOM steps must NOT use `|| true` — failures should be visible
- Run pip-audit and bandit in CI
- Use uv.lock for reproducible installs

## GitHub Actions
- Pin actions to SHA or v4 (e.g. `actions/checkout@v4`)
- Support both `main` and `master` branches where applicable

## Scheduled Workflows
- Use `workflow_dispatch` for manual runs
- Document cron schedule in comments
